PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782370082
OL,3,CFrance confirms first Ebola case in
OL,4,Cdoctor returning from DR Congo
OL,6,FFrench medics have been part of
OL,7,Finternational efforts to treat and
OL,8,Fhelp those affected by the outbreak,
OL,9,Fwhich has continued to present a major
OL,10,Fchallenge.
OL,12,FOn Sunday, confirmed cases in eastern
OL,13,FCongo reached 1,003, including 254
OL,14,Fdeaths, Congo's Ministry of Health
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
