PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782370082
OL,3,CFrance confirms first Ebola case in
OL,4,Cdoctor returning from DR Congo
OL,6,FAuthorities said a total of 100 people
OL,7,Fhave recovered in the outbreak
OL,8,Fconcentrated in the Ituri province
OL,9,Fsince it was declared on May 15, while
OL,10,Fat least 365 patients are in hospitals
OL,11,For in isolation.
OL,13,FThe Ebola outbreak caused by the rare
OL,14,FBundibugyo virus, which has no
OL,15,Fvaccines or treatment, was the worst
OL,16,Fever in its first month.
OL,18,FOfficials admit there could be far
OL,19,Fmore cases they still don't know
OL,20,Fabout, and that the peak of the
OL,21,Foutbreak is still ahead.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782370082
OL,3,CFrance confirms first Ebola case in
OL,4,Cdoctor returning from DR Congo
OL,6,FContact tracing remains a key issue
OL,7,Ffor local authorities, who have only
OL,8,Fachieved a 55% coverage rate, the
OL,9,Fministry said.
OL,11,FOfficials also have yet to identify
OL,12,Fthe patient zero and trace more than
OL,13,F35,000 people who have come in contact
OL,14,Fwith infected individuals as of last
OL,15,Fweek, authorities said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
