PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1782370082
OL,3,CFrance confirms first Ebola case in
OL,4,Cdoctor returning from DR Congo
OL,6,FThe European Centre for Disease
OL,7,FPrevention and Control (ECDC) has
OL,8,Fassessed the risk of infection as low
OL,9,Ffor European residents and travellers
OL,10,Fto areas of active transmission, and
OL,11,Fvery low for the general European
OL,12,Fpopulation.
OL,14,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,15,Fsays that while "the WHO assesses the
OL,16,Frisk of this event as low at a global
OL,17,Flevel, high at the regional level and
OL,18,Fvery high at a national level", the
OL,19,Frisk to the UK population "is assessed
OL,20,Fas low".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
